_:N8d91958cb304431699c318808c3f9313 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"gott-advisory-board\">GOTT Advisory Board</h2>\n\n<p>GOTT’s advisory board supports the Chief Executive and leadership team by advising on long term strategy, annual planning and performance.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"knowledge-assets-network\">Knowledge Assets Network</h2>\n\n<p>The Knowledge Assets Network is a community for those who work with or who want to learn more about Knowledge Assets in central government, arm’s length bodies and public sector research establishments. The <abbr title=\"Knowledge Assets Network\">KAN</abbr> provides a space for members to share advice, best practice, challenges, insights and to learn from one another about Knowledge Asset management.</p>\n\n<p>Visit the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/join-the-knowledge-assets-network-for-the-public-sector/the-knowledge-asset-network\">Knowledge Assets Network</a> for more information.</p>\n\n<p>For questions, email us at <a href=\"mailto:GOTT@dsit.gov.uk\">GOTT@dsit.gov.uk</a>.</p>\n\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
